source.name: Groundfish Observer Maps for Alaska, 1993-2010
source.description: Subset of the Alaska observer groundfish data, aggregating by 400km square cells and eliminating cells with less than 3 vessels to create a public version of the Alaska groundfish observer data. Allows visitors use of the aggregated observer data to create maps. These maps are designed to provide a better understanding of where groundfish are caught in the Aleutian Islands, Bering Sea and Gulf of Alaska.
